* TITLE            : DYNAMICALLY LOAD AND EXECUTE A MODULE     *        00130000
*                                                              *        00140000
* FILE NAME        : CTSALDC                                   *        00150000
*                                                              *        00160000
* AUTHOR           : DORON COHEN                               *        00170000
